title: Lace-Up Wedge Sneakers – Breathable Running Shoes
body_html:
Stay active in style with these unisex lace-up wedge sneakers, perfect for running, walking, or casual wear. Designed for breathability and comfort, these sporty shoes combine a modern look with performance-ready features — ideal for your daily hustle.

✨ Features:

  • Lightweight mesh upper keeps your feet cool and well-ventilated
  • Stylish color matching adds a trendy, athletic touch
  • Lace-up closure ensures a secure, adjustable fit
  • Low wedge heel (1–3 cm) gives subtle elevation without sacrificing comfort
  • Round toe shape for a natural, relaxed fit
  • Unisex design – perfect for both women and men
  • Available in multiple colors – white, red, black, gray, pink, transparent, and champagne
  • Suitable for everyday wear, workouts, or light running

Package Includes:

  • 1 Pair x Shoes

Size Options:

  •  EU Sizes: 35, 36, 37, 38, 39, 40, 41, 42, 43
